    <div class="text-5xl font-bold">Zach Stout</div>
    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">Full Stack Developer</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
       <div class="portfolio-header">
    <p>
        Critical Care Military Nurse turned Software Developer, I've always been dedicated to making a difference. Now, I've channeled that same dedication into the digital world, evolving into a passionate full-stack developer. Combining my meticulous care from the medical field with the technical finesse of software development, I craft solutions that are both intuitive and impactful.
    </p>
</div>

      </text>
